## Purpose

This register records every item of the type above that **{{COMPANY_NAME}}** holds. It is the authoritative list; if an item exists but is not in this register, the register is wrong, not the item.

The register is reviewed at the cadence in the *Operating Cadence*. The owner of the register is recorded in the *Domain and Account Register*.

## Columns

- **Item** — name of the asset / account / contract.
- **Owner** — the person responsible for it.
- **Started** — the date we acquired or signed it.
- **Renewal / review date** — the next date a decision is required.
- **Cost** — annualised cost, in GBP.
- **Notes** — anything relevant: contract reference, contact email, login owner.

